
/**********************************************************************
TorrentFlux-NG Upgrade file
**********************************************************************/

    Contents:
    =========
    1. Introduction
    2. Notes
    3. Upgrade Procedure

/**********************************************************************
1. Introduction
**********************************************************************/

    This is a procedure for updating your database schema if you are 
    already running TorrentFlux-ng from the Epsylon3 repository.


/**********************************************************************
2. Notes
**********************************************************************/

    Note that although it is possible to use the upgraded database both
    for a epsylon3/torrentflux(https://github.com/epsylon3/torrentflux) 
    and a th3penguinwhisperer/torrentflux-ng 
    (https://github.com/torrentflux/TorrentFluxNG)installation.
    However there might be differences in the transferlist that is being
    displayed.


/**********************************************************************
3. Upgrade Procedure
**********************************************************************/

    The upgrade procedure is simple:
    mysql -u dbuser -h iporhostname dbname < sql/upgrade-tf-ng.sql
    This will execute the the sql statements on your database.

